relation: Darrow1 - #32 Jeff and Tony check around and steal some cookies while obtaining information on Maxwell. Fortunately, Maxwell doesn't actually watch the kids and could care less what happens to them!
Darrow1 - #33 Maxwell provides his assistance in the form of a...key? Well, it was a key at one point. Also, a disturbing look into the supposed life of Dr. Andonuts.
Darrow1 - #34 Jeff and Tony bid farewell to Maxwell as they head into the locker room for Jeff to arm up. Tony, of course, is all too excited about the results.
Darrow1 - #35 Jeff makes his way out into the wild, saying farewell to his old pal Tony. Fret not, as our curly haired friend will one day return, perhaps more creepy than usual.

Darrow1 - #36 With both of his friends out of the picture, how is Jeff going to maintain reader interest with a solo character?! Easy! Pick up a monkey that loves gum. Studies show that monkeys increase the chances of hilarity by 100%. That is...the power of monkey.
